OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FWorld heavyweight champion Anthony
OL,7,FJoshua is set to fight Tyson Fury
OL,8,Flater this year after promoter Eddie
OL,9,FHearn confirmed a deal had been signed.
OL,11,FJoshua will first face Albanian
OL,12,Fheavyweight Kristian Prenga in Riyadh
OL,13,Fthis summer, marking a comeback to the
OL,14,Fsport months after he was injured in a
OL,15,Fserious car crash, which killed two of
OL,16,Fhis close friends.
OL,18,FAnnouncing the biggest fight in
OL,19,FBritish boxing history on Instagram,
OL,20,FHearn wrote: "Signed, sealed,
OL,21,Fdelivered! AJ v Fury is on!"
OL,26,@}D@\O]
