OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777334613
OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FHe added: "The biggest piece of
OL,7,Fbusiness we've ever done but more
OL,8,Fimportantly the one we've always
OL,9,Fwanted. Biggest year of AJ's career
OL,10,Fcoming up, the comeback is on."
OL,12,FThe fight between Joshua and Fury is
OL,13,Fdue to take place in November and will
OL,14,Fbe streamed on Netflix.
OL,16,FIt would bring an end to years of back-
OL,17,Fand-forth over a potential showdown
OL,18,Fbetween the two rivals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
