OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777334613
OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FThe warm-up fight with Prenga in Saudi
OL,7,FArabia on 25 July will mark the first
OL,8,Ftime Joshua has stepped into the ring
OL,9,Fsince he was a passenger in a serious
OL,10,Fcar crash in Nigeria in December 2025.
OL,12,FSina Ghami and Latif Ayodele, long-
OL,13,Fterm friends and members of Joshua's
OL,14,Fteam, both died in the incident.
OL,16,FJoshua sustained minor injuries and
OL,17,Fwas taken to hospital to be treated at
OL,18,Fthe time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
