PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777334613
OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FBefore the crash, Joshua's last fight
OL,7,Fwas against the YouTube star Jake
OL,8,FPaul. It lasted just six rounds and
OL,9,Fended with Joshua knocking out Paul.
OL,11,FBut Joshua's fight against the
OL,12,Frelatively unknown Prenga could pose
OL,13,Fan unexpected challenge. The Albanian
OL,14,Fhas only lost one of his twenty-one
OL,15,Ffights. All of his wins have been by
OL,16,Fknockout.
OL,18,FIn preparation, Joshua has turned to
OL,19,Fhis previous rival Oleksandr Usyk for
OL,20,Fhelp. The pair are currently training
OL,21,Ftogether at a camp in Valencia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
