OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777334613
OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FJoshua's last meaningful fight was
OL,7,Fagainst Daniel Dubois in 2024 when he
OL,8,Fwas counted out in the fifth round.
OL,10,FThe 36-year-old underwent elbow
OL,11,Fsurgery and also had a shoulder
OL,12,Finjury, preventing him from returning
OL,13,Fto the ring until his comeback meeting
OL,14,Fwith Paul.
OL,16,FFury's latest comeback from retirement
OL,17,Fis already well underway, however.
OL,18,FEarlier this month, he defeated
OL,19,FDagestani boxer Arslanbek Makhmudov
OL,20,Fwith a unanimous vote from the judges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
