OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777334613
OL,3,CAnthony Joshua to fight Tyson Fury as
OL,4,Clong-awaited comeback confirmed
OL,6,FJoshua, who was ringside at the event,
OL,7,Fgoaded Fury, declaring: "I'm the
OL,8,Flandlord, remember that. You work for
OL,9,Fme." A challenge he repeated in a
OL,10,Fstatement on Monday.
OL,12,F"It's no secret I've taken some time
OL,13,Fto consolidate and rebuild to be ready
OL,14,Ffor stepping back into the ring and
OL,15,Fthis is the next step on that
OL,16,Fjourney," Joshua said.
OL,18,F"I'm looking forward to competing and
OL,19,Fpicking up where I left off. As I
OL,20,Fsaid. The landlord will collect his
OL,21,Frent. That is certain."
